ATTN: Kitten up for adoption!!!! her name is Iris (i call her Borus), shes about 5 months old and is friendly one she get to know you. but she has some problems... first of all she has one eye. its not as creepy as it sounds. it actually makes her cuter. but she also had feline leukimia. so that means you cant have other cats or else they might get infected. feline leukimia is not infectious to humans...dont worry. but she used to be a stray and now she is in need of a home because she cant live at work anymore cause she keeps setting off the alarm. so if you think that mabe you would be able to adopt her, that would be amazing. or if you know anyone who might want to, tell me. the last thing i want is for her to end up in a kennel, and bein put alseep. ill post a picture of her to guilt all you jerks into keeping her. seriously. try and help me find her a home.

aww shit so my thanksgiving rocked. shall we recap? i think so. i woke up at around 1130 which was nice and pushed billy out of his deep sleep. lazy ass. and we made our way over to the reeses where the most delicious breakfast was waiting for us. yumm. even though it was like 130 when we started eating it. so we all hung out and ohh man kevin got some weird creatures that i got to play with. yeah thats right i held a tarantula (sp?). it was awesome. and the guys played ping pong and what not. bill beat me so bad at foos ball. damn. and i improved greatly at mario tennis. yessss. after that we ate dinner at like 4 oclock which was hard since i had just ate an outrageous breakfast. so i didnt eat much. i went home and made some pies with my sisters which was interesting since coralyn cant cook for anything. but dinner was good and the corie gave me a hair cut. which was needed. and i dont know it was a nice family day.

 

the rest of our long weekend flew! friday me and corie hit up the met which was cool, and after i went to corys party. i got there late so alot of people had left but it was still fun. we ended up sleeping over that night cause billy cory and grahm were ddring until what like 6 in the morning. ridiculous! but it was cool. everyone crashed all over the house. we made a not that unconfortable bed on the floor with some blankets. not bad if i do say so myself.

saturday like didnt happen as cory put it. we woke up at 11 and me and bill and mia went to my house and slept till 4 something. oo but me and billy did go to sushi at izumis which was interesting. yeah i made him eat the raw fish. yummm. i dont even remember the rest of that night. but sunday cory needed our help putting together a movie for him. which i told him i wouldnt do but it turned out to be kinda fun. and itcame out cool too. and yeah theres a very sexy scene in it. haha actually its about drugs and me making bill do cocaine and then billy going on this weird trip where we make out and then i eventually take advantage of him. ooooo. but its cool. rated R though. so bring an id. and now our weekend is over and school is back. boooo! i skipped today cause i havent been feeling well. yuck.

i really cant wait for xmas break. im like counting down the days. im joining the gym which is going to rock heavily. and i wont have like 13 hour work days going from school to work every day. its going to be perfect. only like 3 more weeks or something. plus chirstmas. plus new years.
